WEBVTT

01:50.239 --> 01:51.959
Hello, I'm here to pick up my ID card.

01:56.000 --> 01:57.640
Hello, please show your original document.

02:12.599 --> 02:14.599
The first time I made up my life

02:15.400 --> 02:17.120
was in my essay.

02:18.879 --> 02:20.840
I had the world's warmest

02:21.479 --> 02:22.759
and most loving parents.

02:24.919 --> 02:25.879
The first time I invented

02:25.879 --> 02:26.919
my own identity

02:28.199 --> 02:29.479
the apple of their eye.

02:31.199 --> 02:32.120
This child,

02:33.639 --> 02:34.840
If you don't want her, I will.

02:35.960 --> 02:36.919
If you won't raise her,

02:38.120 --> 02:38.919
I will.

02:40.960 --> 02:41.759
Mom.

02:41.919 --> 02:44.280
She has congenital heart disease.

02:44.520 --> 02:46.960
We can't afford her treatment.

02:50.080 --> 02:50.599
Hello.

02:50.639 --> 02:51.800
Here's your new ID card.

02:51.840 --> 02:52.400
Please keep it safe.

02:52.680 --> 02:53.560
The old ID card

02:53.560 --> 02:54.360
can no longer be used.

02:54.479 --> 02:55.599
So we've taken it back.

03:01.840 --> 03:03.560
The second time I made up my life

03:04.319 --> 03:05.560
was on my ID card.

03:06.280 --> 03:08.120
At eighteen, I changed my name.

03:08.800 --> 03:10.840
From Qiao Yan to Xu Yan.

03:12.120 --> 03:13.199
I took my grandmother's surname.

03:13.520 --> 03:15.240
There's only one thing I want to do.

03:16.000 --> 03:17.840
Give my grandmother a good life.

03:21.120 --> 03:22.039
Xu Yan.

03:22.840 --> 03:24.280
That's a beautiful name.

03:24.599 --> 03:26.039
It must have a special meaning.

03:27.840 --> 03:30.199
"Xu" means a promise worth a thousand gold.

03:30.719 --> 03:33.039
"Yan" means beauty and wisdom.

03:33.520 --> 03:34.919
It's our hope for our daughter.

03:34.919 --> 03:35.879
A kind of expectation.

03:38.439 --> 03:39.520
Thank you, Uncle and Auntie,

03:40.120 --> 03:41.439
for letting Yan Yan marry me.

03:42.039 --> 03:43.080
To marry her

03:43.280 --> 03:44.159
is my good fortune.

03:45.840 --> 03:46.520
Haoming,

03:47.120 --> 03:48.840
you're outstanding in every way.

03:49.400 --> 03:50.199
Top schools all the way.

03:50.680 --> 03:51.639
Talented and handsome.

03:52.080 --> 03:52.879
So young,

03:52.919 --> 03:54.000
and already your father's

03:54.039 --> 03:54.719
right-hand man.

03:55.000 --> 03:55.759
That's impressive.

03:57.240 --> 03:59.479
The architecture department at Syracuse University

03:59.800 --> 04:00.560
is very prestigious.

04:00.800 --> 04:01.800
After you arrive,

04:02.039 --> 04:02.759
in the future,

04:02.800 --> 04:04.120
about the future of architecture

04:04.159 --> 04:05.759
and its trends,

04:06.039 --> 04:06.759
I'll surely

04:06.919 --> 04:08.520
ask you for advice.

04:09.479 --> 04:10.960
You're too modest.

04:11.240 --> 04:12.520
Jinda is a top company in the industry.

04:12.520 --> 04:13.759
One of the very best.

04:14.159 --> 04:15.400
Especially in recent years,

04:15.759 --> 04:16.680
leading several

04:16.680 --> 04:18.120
major landmark projects in China.

04:19.240 --> 04:20.240
No matter what,

04:20.600 --> 04:21.600
theory

04:21.800 --> 04:22.560
still needs to guide

04:22.600 --> 04:23.639
our practice.

04:24.800 --> 04:25.399
Recently,

04:25.560 --> 04:27.120
what topics are you researching?

04:29.199 --> 04:31.759
Eviro.

04:32.439 --> 04:33.879
Eviro.

04:34.000 --> 04:34.639
Eviro.

04:35.240 --> 04:36.000
Eviro.

04:36.879 --> 04:37.800
Eviro.

04:40.199 --> 04:41.959
Eviro, biu biu.

04:42.319 --> 04:45.120
Eco-architecture.

04:45.519 --> 04:46.120
Yes, yes.

04:46.439 --> 04:47.000
Yes, yes.

04:47.240 --> 04:48.079
The materials last week

04:48.120 --> 04:49.120
were already sent.

04:49.480 --> 04:51.120
I hope you both can memorize them well.

04:51.480 --> 04:52.839
No surprises, please.

04:53.079 --> 04:53.879
Don't worry, don't worry.

04:54.120 --> 04:55.480
When we get back,

04:59.600 --> 05:00.959
we'll change our shampoo.

05:02.120 --> 05:03.079
The perfume is for you.

05:04.319 --> 05:05.959
Cheap perfume has a strong

05:06.240 --> 05:07.639
alcohol smell.

05:09.279 --> 05:10.319
Let's switch to this tomorrow.

05:10.639 --> 05:11.879
Miss Xu, don't worry.

05:12.000 --> 05:12.800
Words like these,

05:12.920 --> 05:13.759
and the materials,

05:14.040 --> 05:15.720
we'll definitely memorize them thoroughly.

05:15.879 --> 05:16.720
Once we're on site,

05:17.399 --> 05:18.360
we'll recite them backwards.

05:18.519 --> 05:19.399
They'll come out naturally.

05:20.040 --> 05:21.360
Your major is

05:23.240 --> 05:24.600
eco-architecture.

05:25.160 --> 05:26.600
That's also my focus at the studio.

05:26.639 --> 05:28.399
It's the direction I've always researched.

05:29.079 --> 05:30.480
Achieving zero carbon emissions

05:30.480 --> 05:31.279
in eco-architecture.

05:31.439 --> 05:32.920
That's also the main research topic

05:33.040 --> 05:34.879
in the global architecture industry.

05:36.639 --> 05:37.920
With such highly educated parents,

05:38.199 --> 05:39.399
it's no wonder Yan Yan

05:39.519 --> 05:40.720
is such an outstanding daughter.

05:44.439 --> 05:46.040
Syracuse University.

05:46.680 --> 05:47.480
This university

05:47.519 --> 05:49.040
I visited and researched it last year.

05:49.519 --> 05:50.800
The campus cafeteria was terrible.

05:50.920 --> 05:51.879
All Western food.

05:52.399 --> 05:53.920
But on Marshall Street outside,

05:54.040 --> 05:55.160
there's a Chinese restaurant.

05:55.439 --> 05:56.959
Their Beijing Roast Duck is very authentic.

05:57.639 --> 05:58.680
Have you tried it?

06:12.959 --> 06:13.639
Three

06:14.079 --> 06:14.600
Two

06:15.079 --> 06:15.680
One

06:16.120 --> 06:16.759
Smile

06:17.639 --> 06:18.399
Stop taking pictures

06:19.040 --> 06:20.240
You're not here as tourists

06:21.519 --> 06:22.600
On this trip

06:22.800 --> 06:24.279
You'll visit both on and off campus

06:24.560 --> 06:25.480
To deepen your memories

06:26.000 --> 06:27.120
As if you really

06:27.160 --> 06:28.600
lived and worked here

06:28.959 --> 06:29.519
Understand?

06:29.759 --> 06:30.439
Got it

06:30.680 --> 06:31.600
Behind you

06:32.680 --> 06:34.120
Ernest Bird Library

06:34.720 --> 06:36.319
On the right is the law school building

06:37.279 --> 06:39.160
There are only two cafeterias on campus

06:39.199 --> 06:40.360
Fourteen cafés

06:40.439 --> 06:41.680
We usually eat at

06:41.720 --> 06:42.600
Xien Restaurant

06:42.879 --> 06:44.199
The only Chinese restaurant off campus

06:44.240 --> 06:45.199
It has three specialties

06:45.319 --> 06:46.680
Boiled Fish, Mapo Tofu

06:46.759 --> 06:47.600
Spicy Chicken

06:47.879 --> 06:48.800
What's the restaurant called?

06:49.000 --> 06:50.319
Probably P.F.Chang's

06:51.199 --> 06:52.120
Yanyan's dad and I

06:52.199 --> 06:53.600
used to go there often

06:54.000 --> 06:56.360
But that's a Sichuan restaurant

06:56.639 --> 06:58.079
They don't have Beijing Roast Duck

06:58.399 --> 06:59.439
Their signature dish

06:59.639 --> 07:01.040
is Mapo Tofu

07:04.120 --> 07:05.879
Dad's favorite is Boiled Fish

07:06.920 --> 07:07.519
What a pity

07:07.879 --> 07:09.160
It sells out as soon as winter starts

07:09.600 --> 07:10.600
Nowhere is as

07:10.680 --> 07:11.480
abundant as back home

07:11.480 --> 07:11.959
That's true

07:13.600 --> 07:15.399
Sorry, I remembered wrong

07:15.600 --> 07:16.600
Last time I went

07:16.639 --> 07:18.199
I visited so many places, I forgot

07:19.720 --> 07:20.959
But last time I went

07:21.079 --> 07:22.319
I met some Chinese professors

07:22.959 --> 07:24.279
But I didn't see you

07:27.120 --> 07:28.639
I checked on Baidu

07:29.399 --> 07:30.959
but couldn't find your information

07:38.199 --> 07:39.319
Why is that?

07:47.519 --> 07:48.000
Xu Jiajia

07:48.079 --> 07:49.199
Are you really immigrating?

07:49.680 --> 07:50.480
This university

07:50.920 --> 07:52.720
Look, it's so beautiful

07:53.720 --> 07:54.800
All the paperwork is done

07:54.879 --> 07:55.720
I'm leaving next month

07:56.040 --> 07:57.279
I'm so envious

07:57.439 --> 07:58.639
Your parents are university teachers

07:58.759 --> 07:59.439
You can even

07:59.560 --> 08:00.879
study at the same university as them

08:01.720 --> 08:02.720
They're not really teachers

08:03.079 --> 08:04.160
They just work at the research institute

08:04.160 --> 08:05.360
as staff

08:05.920 --> 08:06.519
Abroad

08:06.519 --> 08:07.720
you can only find one name

08:08.040 --> 08:08.800
In China

08:08.879 --> 08:10.160
you can't even find the name

08:14.240 --> 08:14.959
Auntie Yu

08:17.079 --> 08:18.839
My dad doesn't teach classes

08:19.800 --> 08:20.959
He only serves as

08:20.959 --> 08:22.639
a researcher at the campus institute

08:23.040 --> 08:23.680
So

08:24.000 --> 08:25.639
maybe on Baidu in China

08:25.639 --> 08:26.360
you really can't find him

08:39.320 --> 08:39.960
Here you go

08:48.000 --> 08:48.919
We researchers

08:49.000 --> 08:49.720
really aren't as

08:49.759 --> 08:51.320
wealthy or glamorous as those in business

08:52.039 --> 08:52.720
But we also have

08:52.759 --> 08:53.600
our own value

08:54.080 --> 08:54.600
Fame and fortune

08:55.519 --> 08:56.759
aren't my ultimate goal

08:58.080 --> 08:59.159
Yes, that's true

08:59.440 --> 09:01.960
You focus on research

09:02.120 --> 09:02.399
Right?

09:02.440 --> 09:03.480
modest and unassuming

09:03.799 --> 09:06.759
That's a true family of scholars

09:08.840 --> 09:09.679
Sorry

09:10.240 --> 09:11.320
I was being presumptuous

09:17.720 --> 09:18.200
By the way

09:19.960 --> 09:20.759
This is

09:22.159 --> 09:23.720
my recently published humble work

09:23.960 --> 09:24.679
You two

09:25.559 --> 09:26.679
are both professionals in the field

09:26.840 --> 09:27.879
I hope for your guidance

09:28.159 --> 09:28.639
Thank you

09:28.759 --> 09:29.320
Thank you

09:33.840 --> 09:34.519
Look at this handwriting

09:35.200 --> 09:36.480
Cultured people are different

09:36.559 --> 09:37.879
Such beautiful writing

09:40.600 --> 09:41.960
Why don't I have a signature?

09:42.600 --> 09:43.720
Maybe you forgot

09:44.000 --> 09:44.879
Please add it for me

09:45.120 --> 09:46.279
Otherwise, it'd be a pity

09:47.519 --> 09:48.159
Sorry

09:48.360 --> 09:49.519
I was careless

10:08.679 --> 10:10.360
Thank you, Uncle Xu, for your book

10:11.000 --> 10:11.960
And thank you

10:12.279 --> 10:13.559
for bringing gifts from so far away

10:14.000 --> 10:14.519
You went to a lot of trouble

10:14.919 --> 10:15.480
What a shame

10:16.039 --> 10:16.519
Unfortunately

10:16.759 --> 10:17.759
Jiajia went to Paris

10:18.440 --> 10:19.480
I've contacted her

10:20.360 --> 10:21.039
But it's okay

10:21.080 --> 10:22.120
We can meet next time

10:23.039 --> 10:24.600
Uncle, could you sign for me?

10:25.799 --> 10:26.120
Well

10:26.679 --> 10:28.600
I didn't write this book alone

10:28.799 --> 10:29.720
All the researchers

10:29.759 --> 10:30.639
worked on it together

10:31.000 --> 10:32.480
But I only know you

10:33.639 --> 10:34.200
Alright

11:06.440 --> 11:06.919
Here you go

11:07.039 --> 11:07.679
Thank you

11:20.720 --> 11:22.000
Beautiful handwriting

11:22.200 --> 11:22.960
At first glance

11:23.320 --> 11:25.240
it exudes a scholarly vibe

11:26.600 --> 11:27.360
Uncle, Aunt

11:27.679 --> 11:28.480
We've talked for so long

11:28.799 --> 11:29.679
You must be hungry

11:30.159 --> 11:31.360
Let's move to the restaurant

11:31.840 --> 11:33.000
and discuss the wedding arrangements

11:34.039 --> 11:34.679
As for the process

11:34.679 --> 11:36.399
it's best if you decide yourselves

11:36.639 --> 11:37.440
We

11:37.879 --> 11:39.480
can only offer suggestions

11:40.840 --> 11:41.399
This way, please

11:42.600 --> 11:44.039
This area

11:44.559 --> 11:45.720
the biggest advantage

11:45.759 --> 11:46.799
is its location

11:47.039 --> 11:47.600
which is quite good

11:47.759 --> 11:49.240
The only downside here, I think

11:49.240 --> 11:50.600
is that it's not ideal

11:50.639 --> 11:51.799
because it's under the flight path

11:52.039 --> 11:52.600
Sometimes

11:52.679 --> 11:53.679
planes fly overhead

11:53.960 --> 11:54.720
But it's not too bad

11:55.080 --> 11:56.120
It's not that loud, so it's fine

12:02.480 --> 12:03.080
Yanyan

12:04.279 --> 12:05.960
Do you still like the food our chef makes?

12:06.320 --> 12:07.240
Do you still enjoy it?

12:08.320 --> 12:09.080
It's delicious.

12:09.240 --> 12:10.039
Thank you, Auntie.

12:10.639 --> 12:11.559
I'm glad you like it.

12:14.320 --> 12:15.480
You don't like eggs, do you?

12:24.759 --> 12:26.320
Are they your biological parents?

12:31.279 --> 12:32.440
It seems like you and your parents

12:32.480 --> 12:33.240
aren't very close.

12:38.200 --> 12:39.080
As a mother,

12:39.440 --> 12:40.799
not even knowing her daughter doesn't eat eggs—

12:40.840 --> 12:41.600
how could she not know?

12:48.559 --> 12:49.519
Yanyan, come here.

12:52.000 --> 12:52.720
Thank you, Mom.

12:54.440 --> 12:55.039
Yanyan

12:55.120 --> 12:56.159
You should eat a bit more.

13:15.639 --> 13:17.799
Some things can't be faked.

13:18.440 --> 13:19.600
And fake things can't become real.

13:24.279 --> 13:25.399
I want to hear the truth.

13:34.799 --> 13:35.559
Have some more fruit.

13:36.000 --> 13:36.720
Okay, thank you.

13:36.919 --> 13:37.679
Don't be so polite.

13:43.240 --> 13:43.879
I'm sorry.

13:46.919 --> 13:47.799
Sorry for what?

13:51.919 --> 13:52.840
I lied.

13:54.720 --> 13:55.799
What did you lie about?

14:00.480 --> 14:01.600
About having a side project.

14:01.919 --> 14:02.360
I said it was fine.

14:02.360 --> 14:03.039
I told you to take your time learning.

14:03.039 --> 14:04.039
I said we had no chance.

14:04.399 --> 14:05.240
Actually, since I was little,

14:05.279 --> 14:07.039
I was raised by my grandmother.

14:08.759 --> 14:10.279
My parents left for their careers

14:12.519 --> 14:12.960
and left me behind.

14:13.000 --> 14:14.559
They went abroad to work very early on.

14:16.320 --> 14:17.600
So basically,

14:20.120 --> 14:21.480
I hardly ever saw them.

14:25.240 --> 14:27.240
I never really felt

14:29.279 --> 14:29.840
a father's love

14:30.399 --> 14:31.399
or a mother's love.

14:38.360 --> 14:39.279
I made a fuss about it,

14:40.039 --> 14:40.960
argued too,

14:42.639 --> 14:44.039
but it didn't help.

14:46.000 --> 14:47.600
I even didn't want to acknowledge them.

14:48.960 --> 14:49.960
If not for this time—

14:53.200 --> 14:54.480
if it weren't for Haoming,

14:55.519 --> 14:56.639
if it weren't for the wedding,

14:58.440 --> 14:58.919
I think I

14:58.960 --> 15:00.120
wouldn't have contacted them at all.

15:03.320 --> 15:04.720
So when I said before

15:06.120 --> 15:07.840
that I had a harmonious

15:08.399 --> 15:09.559
family relationship,

15:11.879 --> 15:12.960
I was lying.

15:14.320 --> 15:15.600
I'm sorry, Auntie Yu.

15:17.039 --> 15:17.919
I just wanted

15:17.919 --> 15:18.919
to do my best

15:18.960 --> 15:20.000
to make you and Uncle

15:20.039 --> 15:21.639
have a good impression of me.

15:22.000 --> 15:23.559
I wanted you to think

15:24.720 --> 15:25.840
that I grew up

15:28.080 --> 15:30.159
in a loving family.

15:31.039 --> 15:32.159
Not like how things really are.

15:34.799 --> 15:36.000
I wanted you

15:36.799 --> 15:38.440
and Haoming to feel at ease, so—

15:40.360 --> 15:41.120
I'm sorry.

15:48.759 --> 15:50.440
Parents have their own struggles too.

15:53.279 --> 15:54.519
Everyone wants to balance work

15:54.559 --> 15:55.960
and family.

15:57.879 --> 15:59.000
But truly achieving that

16:00.000 --> 16:00.919
isn't easy.

16:02.559 --> 16:03.879
Haoming also grew up

16:04.000 --> 16:05.399
studying abroad alone.

16:06.080 --> 16:07.519
He rarely saw us.

16:08.000 --> 16:10.000
I've always felt I owe him.

16:22.399 --> 16:23.000
Sister Lan,

16:24.440 --> 16:25.559
Chenchen is back from class.

16:26.440 --> 16:27.000
Got it.

16:28.879 --> 16:29.559
I'll go over first.

16:30.200 --> 16:30.960
Auntie Yu,

16:33.559 --> 16:34.320
thank you.

17:10.720 --> 17:11.319
What's wrong?

17:11.759 --> 17:12.279
Sister Yan,

17:12.559 --> 17:13.119
your application to transfer to

17:13.160 --> 17:14.160
the official host of the family banquet

17:14.160 --> 17:14.960
was rejected again.

17:15.319 --> 17:16.640
Sun Siwei found out you applied

17:16.759 --> 17:17.240
and at the director's office

17:17.279 --> 17:18.319
she really lost her temper.

17:18.559 --> 17:19.519
You'd better be careful.

17:22.200 --> 17:23.799
This is just the beginning.

17:25.359 --> 17:26.240
This matter

17:28.559 --> 17:29.799
is far from settled.

17:30.640 --> 17:31.240
Yanyan

17:31.599 --> 17:32.680
come have some fruit.

17:40.279 --> 17:40.799
Coming.

17:48.920 --> 17:49.240
Here.

17:49.880 --> 17:50.640
Miss Xu,

17:51.680 --> 17:52.400
today went

17:52.400 --> 17:53.359
pretty smoothly.

17:54.359 --> 17:55.079
I'll handle the check-out procedures

17:55.119 --> 17:56.160
for you.

17:56.799 --> 17:57.799
Just leave the room card

17:58.039 --> 17:59.319
at the front desk tomorrow morning and you can go.

18:00.160 --> 18:01.400
Try not to go out much during this period.

18:02.160 --> 18:03.400
I'll contact you before the wedding.

18:03.440 --> 18:03.960
After the wedding,

18:04.000 --> 18:05.640
your part will be done.

18:06.279 --> 18:07.000
After that,

18:08.160 --> 18:09.400
we won't trouble you anymore.

18:10.480 --> 18:10.920
Alright.

18:10.920 --> 18:11.599
Understood, understood.

18:11.720 --> 18:12.839
Don't worry.

18:12.920 --> 18:14.359
We're all just faces for hire.

18:14.519 --> 18:15.960
Even if you see us on the street

18:16.039 --> 18:16.599
in the future,

18:16.720 --> 18:17.720
you won't recognize us.

18:18.039 --> 18:18.680
That's right, that's right.

18:19.400 --> 18:20.200
Since we've

18:20.240 --> 18:21.559
taken this job for you,

18:21.680 --> 18:23.480
we definitely won't cause you any trouble.

18:23.640 --> 18:24.240
Rest assured.

18:24.680 --> 18:25.240
Yes, exactly.

18:26.359 --> 18:26.799
Alright.

18:26.920 --> 18:27.440
By the way,

18:27.880 --> 18:28.559
Miss Xu,

18:30.480 --> 18:31.960
take a look at these extras.

18:32.240 --> 18:32.839
I've already

18:32.880 --> 18:34.039
screened them in advance.

18:34.200 --> 18:35.519
See if they can be

18:35.720 --> 18:36.559
banquet guests.

18:37.680 --> 18:39.519
You'll get every cent you're owed.

18:40.680 --> 18:42.160
Don't worry about anything else.

18:43.559 --> 18:44.039
Understood.

18:44.200 --> 18:44.880
Understood, understood.

18:49.279 --> 18:50.440
Check out before 7 a.m. tomorrow.

18:51.279 --> 18:51.920
I'm leaving.

18:53.000 --> 18:53.319
Well then,

18:53.319 --> 18:54.319
Miss Xu, take care.

18:54.440 --> 18:55.200
Take it easy.

19:07.880 --> 19:09.519
A life built on lies—

19:10.759 --> 19:11.680
I gave it my all

19:11.680 --> 19:12.880
to make it a fortress.

19:14.400 --> 19:15.680
But on the sand,

19:16.640 --> 19:18.039
how can there ever be a castle?

19:36.720 --> 19:37.640
Everything

19:37.680 --> 19:39.480
needs to be sorted and arranged properly.

19:40.079 --> 19:40.920
The salad ingredients

19:40.960 --> 19:42.119
and what we need for today

19:42.359 --> 19:43.359
some recipe items

19:43.359 --> 19:44.599
all need to be organized.

19:45.960 --> 19:46.359
Come on.

19:46.759 --> 19:47.440
Wash this thoroughly.

19:52.640 --> 19:53.160
Huanhuan

19:54.960 --> 19:55.680
The guest is ready with makeup.

19:55.759 --> 19:56.960
They've been waiting for over an hour.

19:56.960 --> 19:57.640
Why hasn't Sun Siwei

19:57.680 --> 19:58.319
arrived yet?

19:58.480 --> 19:58.759
Sis,

19:58.759 --> 20:00.000
I've already gone up to remind her twice.

20:00.279 --> 20:00.720
Then get someone

20:00.720 --> 20:01.640
to invite her, okay?

20:01.640 --> 20:02.079
I...

20:02.200 --> 20:03.960
You were the one who called Sun Siwei.

20:08.079 --> 20:08.920
Sorry, Siwei.

20:09.480 --> 20:10.480
Why don't we first

20:10.519 --> 20:12.680
Do you know why you can't replace me

20:12.759 --> 20:13.960
as the host?

20:15.319 --> 20:16.839
Because all you do is

20:16.920 --> 20:18.240
play petty tricks behind the scenes.

20:18.359 --> 20:20.119
It's not presentable at all.

20:21.799 --> 20:24.200
A planner wants to be a host?

20:24.759 --> 20:26.440
You should see if you're even qualified.

20:26.960 --> 20:27.880
Besides,

20:28.680 --> 20:30.680
you can't even handle the planning job.

20:30.720 --> 20:32.119
How is the script written?

20:33.000 --> 20:34.599
The lines are so awkward, how am I supposed to read them?

20:35.240 --> 20:36.680
Every time we record,

20:36.720 --> 20:37.200
this script

20:37.240 --> 20:38.480
is useless to me.

20:38.519 --> 20:39.759
I have to improvise everything.

20:40.359 --> 20:41.200
The celebrity guests you invite

20:41.279 --> 20:42.279
get worse every episode.

20:42.559 --> 20:43.160
The topics you propose

20:43.200 --> 20:44.319
are more boring each time.

20:44.359 --> 20:44.960
With this,

20:46.200 --> 20:47.400
you still want to be the host?

20:51.160 --> 20:51.759
Siwei,

20:53.480 --> 20:54.319
if there's anything in the script

20:54.359 --> 20:55.160
you don't like,

20:55.200 --> 20:56.039
I can go and

20:56.079 --> 20:56.799
change it right now.

20:57.160 --> 20:57.640
But

20:58.720 --> 20:59.960
some guests have mentioned

21:00.039 --> 21:01.440
that the live interview content

21:01.480 --> 21:02.680
doesn't match the script.

21:02.799 --> 21:03.599
What do you mean?

21:03.960 --> 21:05.279
Are you blaming me now?

21:06.559 --> 21:07.480
What's wrong?

21:07.759 --> 21:09.160
I heard you landed a rich boyfriend.

21:09.160 --> 21:11.119
Think you can turn your life around now?

21:15.759 --> 21:18.319
You'd better know your place.

21:19.799 --> 21:21.079
People like them

21:21.559 --> 21:22.759
have a shelf life for relationships

21:22.799 --> 21:24.119
of just a month or two.

21:25.920 --> 21:27.359
If you have energy to spare,

21:27.400 --> 21:29.319
use it to please me instead.

21:30.480 --> 21:31.960
I'm in charge of this show.

21:32.759 --> 21:34.880
One word from me and you're out.

21:37.640 --> 21:38.880
Why hasn't the guest arrived yet?

21:41.920 --> 21:43.160
The weekly ratings report is out.

21:44.680 --> 21:45.400
See for yourself.

21:48.319 --> 21:49.039
Director Zhou,

21:50.599 --> 21:52.039
the ratings for this episode are low.

21:52.119 --> 21:53.039
I take responsibility.

21:53.400 --> 21:54.599
Regarding the guest,

21:55.000 --> 21:56.799
I've communicated with the host.

21:56.920 --> 21:58.200
But she...

22:00.240 --> 22:01.880
So could you please

22:01.920 --> 22:02.839
talk to her?

22:02.960 --> 22:03.599
Xiao Xu,

22:04.119 --> 22:05.480
I understand your difficulties.

22:05.880 --> 22:06.920
But a show

22:06.960 --> 22:09.000
needs everyone's cooperation.

22:09.680 --> 22:12.200
As the planner, you need to see the bigger picture.

22:13.160 --> 22:14.160
Am I right?

22:14.519 --> 22:15.759
Have you decided on the next guest?

22:16.480 --> 22:17.240
Yes.

22:18.440 --> 22:20.319
I'm contacting the founder of Sanmu Art Museum

22:20.359 --> 22:21.880
Mr. Sanmu.

22:22.359 --> 22:23.519
Inviting him to the show.

22:25.759 --> 22:26.480
He agreed to come.

22:27.160 --> 22:28.440
Mr. Sanmu is very interested.

22:28.640 --> 22:29.759
He wants to check

22:29.960 --> 22:30.599
the full schedule.

22:30.599 --> 22:31.799
So it's not confirmed yet.

22:32.640 --> 22:33.319
Xu Yan,

22:34.039 --> 22:35.359
you've worked here for a long time.

22:35.480 --> 22:36.920
You should know very well

22:37.240 --> 22:39.200
you're the planner for the Family Banquet show.

22:39.400 --> 22:42.240
Your job is to plan the show well.

22:42.440 --> 22:43.359
Build a lineup

22:43.359 --> 22:45.119
of guests the audience loves.

22:46.079 --> 22:47.079
As for becoming the host,

22:47.799 --> 22:49.319
haste makes waste.

22:51.640 --> 22:52.559
Let me remind you,

22:53.359 --> 22:55.359
if next week's ratings drop again,

22:58.039 --> 22:59.279
management will consider your position.

22:59.279 --> 23:00.000
They'll be making a decision.

23:16.440 --> 23:17.240
I'm not done yet.

23:18.240 --> 23:19.400
The guest for the next episode

23:19.440 --> 23:20.480
isn't confirmed.

23:20.519 --> 23:21.200
So

23:21.759 --> 23:23.240
all scripts need to be backed up.

23:37.400 --> 23:39.079
I've been contacting him for a long time.

23:40.680 --> 23:41.240
Mr. Sanmu

23:41.279 --> 23:42.799
is a friend I met in London.

23:44.279 --> 23:45.039
This art museum

23:45.039 --> 23:46.240
is his private collection.

23:47.319 --> 23:48.319
I've arranged for you to meet him.

23:48.720 --> 23:49.559
He'll get in touch with you.

23:51.079 --> 23:51.960
Thank you.

23:52.000 --> 23:52.680
You're welcome.

23:53.799 --> 23:54.799
Let me note it down too.

23:54.799 --> 23:55.720
His phone number.

24:00.839 --> 24:01.519
How did you know

24:01.519 --> 24:02.720
my work schedule?

24:07.960 --> 24:09.039
Because on your side

24:09.720 --> 24:10.759
I have an informant.

24:26.440 --> 24:27.079
By the way,

24:28.720 --> 24:29.880
I wanted to ask you,

24:33.279 --> 24:35.640
your parents met my family yesterday.

24:36.680 --> 24:37.759
What did they think?

24:42.920 --> 24:44.200
No matter what they think,

24:45.519 --> 24:46.680
I'm very satisfied.

25:07.319 --> 25:08.440
Do you really love me?

25:10.559 --> 25:11.160
Of course.

25:13.799 --> 25:14.559
What do you love about me?

25:15.400 --> 25:16.000
Everything.

25:18.440 --> 25:19.400
I know very well

25:20.279 --> 25:21.240
that this man in front of me

25:21.240 --> 25:22.240
fulfills all my

25:22.279 --> 25:23.240
expectations of a husband.

25:37.640 --> 25:38.799
I love Shen Haoming.

25:40.240 --> 25:41.119
He's the first

25:41.119 --> 25:42.680
to make me truly feel

25:43.720 --> 25:44.279
loved

25:44.720 --> 25:46.400
and chosen without hesitation.

25:48.839 --> 25:50.480
No matter how many obstacles there are,

25:52.119 --> 25:54.160
I will hold on tightly to this love.

26:18.519 --> 26:18.920
Morning.

26:19.319 --> 26:19.960
Good morning.

26:26.640 --> 26:27.119
Sister Yan

26:27.480 --> 26:28.680
Here's the proposal you asked for yesterday.

26:28.759 --> 26:29.400
Thank you.

26:29.920 --> 26:30.839
There's one more thing.

26:31.279 --> 26:32.359
That trendy plant brand,

26:32.400 --> 26:33.319
the owner of the themed store,

26:33.480 --> 26:34.480
is all about being mysterious.

26:34.759 --> 26:35.680
I've tried calling,

26:35.839 --> 26:36.400
emailing,

26:36.480 --> 26:38.119
and even visiting in person, but all were refused.

26:38.240 --> 26:39.759
They won't accept any interviews.

26:40.480 --> 26:42.200
We're filming in two days.

26:42.359 --> 26:43.039
What should we do?

26:47.279 --> 26:48.599
Let me figure something out. Don't worry.

26:48.759 --> 26:49.599
I'm counting on you.

27:48.400 --> 27:48.880
This way.

27:57.279 --> 27:57.960
Please come this way.

28:02.240 --> 28:03.160
Watch your step.

28:24.200 --> 28:24.799
Be careful.

29:04.720 --> 29:05.519
Hello, boss.

29:06.119 --> 29:07.640
I'm here for the interview today.

29:07.960 --> 29:08.559
Amy.

29:11.240 --> 29:12.400
Take the agave on the table

29:12.599 --> 29:13.359
trim the roots and repot it.

29:16.039 --> 29:16.640
Okay.

29:21.559 --> 29:22.599
Your resume says

29:23.079 --> 29:24.519
you've worked with agave for a long time.

29:24.720 --> 29:25.799
Actually, not that long.

29:26.759 --> 29:28.519
Compared to you, boss,

29:29.119 --> 29:30.480
I'm nothing in comparison.

29:31.039 --> 29:32.839
Not many women like agave.

29:33.480 --> 29:34.720
Why are you interested in it?

29:38.480 --> 29:40.240
Because it has extraordinary vitality.

29:41.720 --> 29:43.079
It's an artist of the earth.

29:43.359 --> 29:44.480
A masterpiece a hundred million years in the making.

29:51.799 --> 29:53.160
It existed alongside dinosaurs.

29:53.640 --> 29:55.240
It grows among rocks and mountains.

29:55.960 --> 29:57.119
Enduring wind and rain.

29:58.039 --> 29:59.119
Its shape

29:59.559 --> 30:01.640
is similar to the legendary dragon's tongue.

30:01.799 --> 30:02.599
Very much alike.

30:04.000 --> 30:05.359
But most importantly,

30:07.279 --> 30:08.440
I can make it

30:08.880 --> 30:10.559
grow the way I want.

30:20.079 --> 30:22.200
Every plant cultivator

30:22.839 --> 30:24.400
has their own perspective.

30:25.119 --> 30:26.480
Some people prefer

30:27.000 --> 30:27.880
natural growth.

30:28.799 --> 30:29.920
Others

30:30.079 --> 30:32.200
like to control it artificially.

30:32.759 --> 30:34.240
My view is

30:36.480 --> 30:37.920
I must make it grow into

30:38.039 --> 30:39.200
the shape I like.

30:53.559 --> 30:55.000
So I use strong light

30:55.000 --> 30:56.519
to limit its leaf growth.

30:57.160 --> 30:59.480
I control the frequency of fertilizing and watering,

30:59.960 --> 31:01.920
as well as soil and ventilation.

31:02.960 --> 31:04.559
Every tiny change in it

31:05.000 --> 31:05.839
must

31:05.880 --> 31:07.200
be within my control.

31:07.599 --> 31:08.640
Because only then

31:08.920 --> 31:10.640
can it reach its full potential.

31:11.559 --> 31:12.720
Start work tomorrow.

31:18.480 --> 31:19.079
Okay.

31:20.480 --> 31:21.920
But if you work here,

31:23.599 --> 31:24.839
what about your other job?

31:24.960 --> 31:25.519
Miss Xu,

31:35.359 --> 31:36.240
Miss Xu Yan,

31:36.880 --> 31:38.079
you're very smart.

31:39.480 --> 31:41.319
Your show is well done.

31:42.759 --> 31:43.759
Your acting is top-notch.

31:45.400 --> 31:46.519
To get close to me,

31:47.880 --> 31:49.000
you learned so much

31:49.079 --> 31:50.160
about agave.

31:51.079 --> 31:51.920
You even practiced

31:52.359 --> 31:53.599
how to cultivate it.

31:54.759 --> 31:56.519
You kept it all secret quite well.

31:58.359 --> 32:00.599
From your clothes and resume,

32:02.359 --> 32:03.039
an ordinary person

32:03.839 --> 32:05.559
would never know you're pretending.

32:06.640 --> 32:07.519
But unfortunately,

32:12.319 --> 32:13.079
you kept contacting

32:13.119 --> 32:14.480
our assistant Huanhuan.

32:15.240 --> 32:16.160
On Weibo,

32:17.079 --> 32:18.240
she posted a photo of you two.

32:26.920 --> 32:28.519
But your views on agave

32:30.519 --> 32:31.359
really moved me.

32:32.559 --> 32:33.519
Still, as I said before,

32:34.440 --> 32:36.160
I won't accept any interviews.

32:37.319 --> 32:38.119
Please go home.

32:44.119 --> 32:45.599
I'm very sorry, Mr. Shen.

32:47.000 --> 32:47.720
For

32:49.920 --> 32:52.119
meeting you in this way.

32:53.400 --> 32:54.319
Regarding the interview,

32:55.720 --> 32:56.920
I respect your

32:58.559 --> 32:59.720
decision.

33:02.640 --> 33:03.880
But before this,

33:03.960 --> 33:05.480
I prepared a gift for you.

33:05.599 --> 33:06.680
I wanted to give it to you in person.

33:13.000 --> 33:14.480
A famous botanist,

33:14.480 --> 33:15.359
Professor Yiding,

33:15.480 --> 33:16.799
personally made these scissors.

33:17.519 --> 33:18.640
They should

33:19.720 --> 33:21.119
match your taste.

33:22.720 --> 33:23.119
Miss,

33:23.279 --> 33:24.640
You've been here many times.

33:24.759 --> 33:26.519
Still haven't found one you like?

33:27.839 --> 33:29.240
I'm indecisive.

33:29.640 --> 33:30.279
I'll look a bit more.

33:30.359 --> 33:31.119
No problem.

33:31.240 --> 33:32.000
Take your time.

33:32.039 --> 33:33.039
Let me know if you need anything.

33:33.119 --> 33:33.559
Thank you.

33:35.880 --> 33:36.799
So careless.

33:37.240 --> 33:38.519
Quick, take it to the back.

33:42.319 --> 33:42.920
Um...

33:44.279 --> 33:44.920
Let me help you.

33:44.920 --> 33:45.480
Yes, yes.

33:45.480 --> 33:45.839
I'll help you.

33:46.000 --> 33:46.880
If this gets lost,

33:46.920 --> 33:47.440
our boss

33:47.480 --> 33:48.640
would definitely fire me.

33:50.440 --> 33:51.400
Is it really that important?

33:51.920 --> 33:52.559
You have no idea.

33:52.680 --> 33:53.680
This is our boss's

33:53.720 --> 33:54.640
personal soil fork.

33:54.880 --> 33:55.960
Made by Professor Yiding.

33:56.200 --> 33:57.200
It's very precious.

34:08.360 --> 34:09.440
Looks like you really

34:10.119 --> 34:11.400
did your homework on me.

34:11.840 --> 34:12.719
But

34:14.159 --> 34:15.280
it doesn't seem to help much.

34:15.960 --> 34:17.039
Don't say that.

34:19.039 --> 34:20.400
Such a valuable limited edition,

34:20.480 --> 34:21.400
and you managed to find it.

34:22.840 --> 34:24.880
Shows you put in a lot of effort.

34:25.960 --> 34:27.400
I have a gift for you too.

34:32.559 --> 34:33.760
Thank you, Mr. Shen.

34:35.760 --> 34:36.719
Open it and take a look.

34:45.320 --> 34:46.559
Is it a coincidence?

34:47.039 --> 34:47.840
Of course not.

34:56.960 --> 34:58.440
Everything I do

35:00.199 --> 35:02.199
is under Mr. Shen's control.

35:03.280 --> 35:04.320
Such a beautiful person

35:04.360 --> 35:05.400
often comes to my shop.

35:06.639 --> 35:08.039
How could that not attract attention?

35:10.480 --> 35:12.480
I thought I was being discreet.

35:13.679 --> 35:15.199
I didn't expect you had allowed it.

35:17.000 --> 35:18.599
Mr. Shen likes

35:19.079 --> 35:20.639
to take the initiative, right?

35:21.960 --> 35:23.480
I've read your articles online.

35:27.039 --> 35:28.480
My grandma has poor eyesight.

35:29.119 --> 35:30.119
But early in the morning,

35:30.480 --> 35:32.039
she starts collecting osmanthus flowers.

35:33.360 --> 35:34.960
When I come home from school,

35:35.719 --> 35:36.679
from a distance,

35:37.199 --> 35:39.679
I see her through the window.

35:41.800 --> 35:43.000
Wearing reading glasses,

35:44.280 --> 35:46.199
she bakes the flower petals.

35:47.679 --> 35:48.639
She told me

35:50.119 --> 35:51.559
if the season passes,

35:52.599 --> 35:53.960
osmanthus jam won't be sweet anymore.

35:55.880 --> 35:57.360
If your grandma

35:57.719 --> 36:00.400
also made osmanthus jam for you,

36:02.400 --> 36:03.360
I don't think

36:03.920 --> 36:05.840
you would have a lonely heart.

36:12.800 --> 36:15.039
Your writing is full of emotion.

36:15.880 --> 36:17.000
It really moved me.

36:18.880 --> 36:19.800
I believe

36:21.519 --> 36:23.199
you must love osmanthus jam.

36:36.400 --> 36:37.280
What?

36:37.719 --> 36:38.960
You were found out.

36:40.599 --> 36:41.920
Did he give you a hard time?

36:43.639 --> 36:44.880
No, he didn't.

36:46.679 --> 36:48.360
But he still refused the interview.

36:49.719 --> 36:50.880
He's really stubborn.

36:54.159 --> 36:55.320
I wouldn't say that.

36:55.840 --> 36:56.880
Maybe

36:57.400 --> 36:59.119
he has his own difficulties.

36:59.360 --> 37:00.000
Or

37:00.400 --> 37:01.000
Wait a minute.

37:07.679 --> 37:08.400
Yan,

37:08.800 --> 37:09.800
are you catching a cold?

37:10.079 --> 37:11.079
You need to take care of yourself.

37:11.199 --> 37:11.840
Get some rest early.

37:11.920 --> 37:12.599
I know.

37:12.760 --> 37:13.320
I'm hanging up.

38:03.800 --> 38:04.360
Yan,

38:04.639 --> 38:06.000
You look worse and worse.

38:06.119 --> 38:07.199
Go home and rest.

38:07.920 --> 38:08.559
I can handle it.

38:12.639 --> 38:13.639
Then take care of yourself.

38:13.960 --> 38:15.039
Call me if you need anything.

38:18.360 --> 38:18.920
Xu Yan,

38:21.039 --> 38:22.119
the owner of the trendy plant shop.

38:22.159 --> 38:23.000
Did you interview him?

38:23.559 --> 38:24.280
Sorry,

38:24.960 --> 38:25.920
I haven't had the chance yet.

38:26.079 --> 38:27.199
Not yet.

38:27.800 --> 38:29.000
The show is about to start recording.

38:29.039 --> 38:30.199
How long do you want to wait?

38:34.119 --> 38:34.599
I'll do it as soon as possible.

38:34.639 --> 38:35.320
What do you mean?

38:35.880 --> 38:36.360
Sick.

38:36.599 --> 38:37.360
Don't want to work anymore.

38:37.519 --> 38:38.480
Want to go home and rest.

38:39.400 --> 38:40.079
Alright.

38:40.840 --> 38:42.280
Go settle your salary.

38:42.320 --> 38:43.480
Then rest at home for good.

38:43.760 --> 38:45.239
Don't say I didn't warn you.

38:45.559 --> 38:46.880
I told you last week.

38:47.039 --> 38:48.360
If the director blames you,

38:48.400 --> 38:49.280
it's not my responsibility.

39:03.159 --> 39:03.920
I have time today

39:03.960 --> 39:05.119
to accept your interview.

39:10.480 --> 39:11.599
Come find me at Jinda Group.

39:12.239 --> 39:13.719
Please contact Casey at the front desk.

39:15.880 --> 39:16.920
Jinda Group.

39:27.559 --> 39:28.159
Hello.

39:28.840 --> 39:30.280
I have an appointment with Mr. Shen Haoming.

39:30.320 --> 39:30.880
Excuse me,

39:30.920 --> 39:31.400
Hello.

39:31.599 --> 39:32.559
Are you Miss Xu?

39:32.639 --> 39:34.199
Mr. Shen is waiting for you upstairs.

39:34.239 --> 39:34.880
Please follow me.

39:35.559 --> 39:36.079
Yueyue,

39:37.400 --> 39:37.920
This way.

39:40.199 --> 39:40.960
Sorry.

39:41.000 --> 39:42.079
I just want to confirm

39:42.920 --> 39:44.519
the Mr. Shen you mentioned

39:44.639 --> 39:45.440
is the one I'm looking for,

39:45.440 --> 39:46.519
Mr. Shen Haoming?

39:46.639 --> 39:47.159
Yes.

39:47.199 --> 39:47.840
Mr. Shen

39:47.880 --> 39:49.360
is our group's Vice President.

39:49.400 --> 39:51.000
He's also Chairman Shen's eldest son.

40:00.039 --> 40:00.719
This way, please.

40:08.599 --> 40:09.039
Please.

40:28.920 --> 40:30.079
Then come back here.

40:31.920 --> 40:32.519
Miss Xu,

40:33.000 --> 40:34.000
Mr. Shen is in a meeting.

40:34.159 --> 40:35.320
Please wait here for a moment.
